 ('25', '25', 'fi_fi', 'Tervetuloa!', '<p>Nyt se on vihdoin julkista, nimittäin nämä sivut joita on tehty uudelleen ja uudelleen kerran toisen jälkeen. Nyt olen tähän versioon tyytyväinen. Aina kun itselleen tekee jotain suhtautuu siihen todella kriittisesti ja tekemisestä ei meinaa tulla oikein mitään. </p>\n<p>Nämä sivut tulevat sisältämään videota, podcasteja ja perinteisiä blogi artikkeleita. </p>\n<p><br /></p>\n<blockquote>Back in July, I had a racist encounter. I say “encounter” because when you have skin as light as mine, experiences with racism can feel pretty alien. I don’t think about the incident often, but certain things — like aged subway stations or eggs Benedict on waffles — conjure up the memory. Lately, I’ve found myself eating a lot of eggs and doing a lot of thinking.</blockquote>\n<p>Mitäs tässä tämä aloitetaan katsomaan hieman koodia.</p><pre>\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt; </pre>', NULL, '0', 'Vihdoinkin olen saanut tehtyä sivut josta löytää kattavasti tietoa koodaukseen. ', '2017-01-01 20:05:46', '2017-03-05 17:58:48', '27ea998a-f19a-459e-9330-3f141f84faef'),
 ('26', '26', 'fi_fi', 'What I learned from my racist run-in (illustrated)', '<p>Back in July, I had a racist encounter. I say “encounter” because when you have skin as light as mine, experiences with racism can feel pretty alien. I don’t think about the incident often, but certain things — like aged subway stations or eggs Benedict on waffles — conjure up the memory. Lately, I’ve found myself eating a lot of eggs and doing a lot of thinking.</p>\n<p><br /></p>\n<p>My boyfriend and I hop on the subway. The man standing next to us strikes up a conversation. We laugh and chat, enjoying the company of a stranger. Then the man begins to speculate about my white boyfriend’s background, to which he responds that he’s British. Then it’s my turn. “And you, you must be Portuguese or Italian,” the man says. “I’m actually Persian — Iranian.” The man turns to my boyfriend. “Be careful. She’s going to blow up.”<br /></p>', NULL, '0', 'Buttons like you’ve never seen them before! Probably.', '2017-03-05 17:23:17', '2017-03-05 17:44:20', 'e2a48463-7070-4920-a1e8-69dfad294b05'),
 ('27', '27', 'fi_fi', 'Yleinen', NULL, 'general', '0', NULL, '2017-03-05 17:49:52', '2017-03-05 17:49:52', 'a308ff44-9ef5-4d58-b413-1a7361f5a09e');



